Author: khakitomatoes
Text: Maybe Hannah is taller than you? Maybe for her 120 is a low weight so she thought it was a compliment.  Honestly no one can accurately guess your weight because people expect adults to weigh (alot) more than 95 lbs.

Author: nasihljeung
Text: i'm so sorry :(( if anything, a lot of people's perception of weight is different, i used to be thrown into a lot of unwanted social situations and always got random numbers thrown at me that varied like 30-40lbs across them all
